{
  "chapter": 110,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述徐子陵与寇仲分头行动的故事。徐子陵藏身飞马牧场一处屋内横梁，发现三执事陶叔盛暗中向外发射信号企图叛变，遂出手将其制服。商秀洵等人被四大寇追击，退入经鲁妙子设计的地下密室。徐子陵自告奋勇留下断后，以怪异真气和刚猛拳劲击退多名贼寇，四大寇之首曹应龙和向霸天在门外叫阵。与此同时，寇仲潜伏在牧场疏林中，目睹李天凡、沈落雁等人假扮牧场人员，企图诱骗李秀宁赴约后将其绑架。寇仲在关键时刻现身，当众揭露假商震（陈老师）和苑儿的真面目，以井中月一刀击杀一名偷袭者，震慑全场。沈落雁与寇仲旧识相见，言语间暗藏复杂情感。寇仲霸气宣战，誓要除沈军师外格杀勿论，李秀宁目睹寇仲威霸气概，心中泛起微妙情愫。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "陶叔盛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柳执事究竟干甚么的，到现在仍未率人来援？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_tao_shu_sheng",
      "text": "闭嘴！柳执事必须避过敌人的主力，才能依计赶来。这着诱敌之计乃没有办法中的办法。谁叫我们错估敌人的实力，以致进退失据。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "馥大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有人过来了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我绝非贼方的人，更全无恶意，现在下来了！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "刚才鄙人冒险发言惊扰，场主可知是甚么原因呢？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若朋友不先表明身分，一切免谈。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "场主只要派人搜索贵属怀内之物，便明白我的说话！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "朋友意思是指他乃叛徒吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "适才我见他欲把烟花火炮一类的东西投往窗外，咦！有人来呢！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快入地道！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "朋友！下来吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "我留此对付敌人，场主记得关上入口。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "商秀洵，有胆就滚出来和曹某见个真章。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_ba_tian",
      "speaker_name": "向霸天",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你是何人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是甚么人，你连问的资格也没有！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大管家你好！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "陈老师",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "这都是随我多年的心腹手下，宁公主可以放心。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_chen_lao_shi",
      "text": "要劳烦大管家从东峡抽身赶回来，秀宁真过意不去，为何诸位不用马匹代步呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "陈老师",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "还不是为了掩人耳目，唉！咦！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公主啊！对不起，我解完手了！真舒服！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "都着你不用来了，你听不到吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "公主息怒！公主息怒！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公主恕罪，请先让小人引介，嘿！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位是李天凡公子，乃瓦岗寨密公的独子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位俏夫人乃真大管家新纳之妾，以前的身分却是李公子的女…啊！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位假冒大管家的人叫陈老师，至于大名嘛…哼！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不要装神弄鬼了，你的好兄弟呢？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "因他怕了你，所以躲起来哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "教他出来杀了我吧！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁舍得杀有沉鱼落雁之容的沈军师呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除沈军师外，其他一个不留？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 288
    }
  ],
